txt.en: You have defeated the morroval Carchrien, Queen of Fangs, at the Sword-hall of Dol Guldur.
You have defeated Durkâr, most terrible of Gertheryg, at the Sword-hall of Dol Guldur.
The Sword-hall of Dol Guldur is presided over by many champions, who train the soldiers of the Enemy.
You have defeated the sorcerer Urcheron at the Sword-hall of Dol Guldur.
